Spam/


## Notification
## None of the above categories sends any notification at all

:0 ic:
| notify-send -a 'Correo nuevo: ' "$(grep "^From:\|^To:\|^Subject:")"


## GitHub issues

:0:
* ^From:.*notifications@github.com
Inbox/
